parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to stall or not start, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Key gets stuck in the ignition
key falls out of the ignition
vehicle stalls or won't start
ignition switch locks up
and electrical burning smell.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the heater and defroster can cause visibility hazards, making it difficult to drive safely.
symptoms: No heat
cold air blows
defroster doesn't work
windows won't defrost
and mist comes from the vents.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause fires, accidents, or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Smoke from under the hood
electrical wires on fire
automatic starter malfunction
and burning smell.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Anti-lock Braking System (ABS) and Traction Control Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS and traction control can cause accidents, especially on wet or slippery roads.
symptoms: ABS and traction control lights come on
knocking sound from the front end
vibration on the brake pedal
and pulsation on the brake pedal.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the doors and windows can cause injuries, especially if the windows close suddenly.
symptoms: Passenger side window goes up and down spontaneously
door wiring breaks
and door components fail.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the heater blend door can cause the heater to malfunction, leading to inadequate defrosting and defogging of the windshield, which can impair the driver's visibility and increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The heater blows cold air
the defroster does not work
the temperature control does not respond
the blend door actuator is faulty
and the vehicle's dashboard needs to be removed to access the faulty part.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to lock up or become difficult to turn, making it hard to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The steering wheel feels hard to turn
the steering wheel locks up
the vehicle is difficult to steer
unusual noises or vibrations when turning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column can cause the steering wheel to lock up or become difficult to turn, making it hard to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The steering wheel feels hard to turn
the steering wheel locks up
the vehicle is difficult to steer
unusual noises or vibrations when turning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition and steering system can cause the steering wheel to lock up or become difficult to turn, making it hard to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The steering wheel feels hard to turn
the steering wheel locks up
the vehicle is difficult to steer
unusual noises or vibrations when turning
the key gets stuck in the ignition.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the wheel bearings can cause the vehicle to vibrate or pull to one side, making it hard to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle vibrates or pulls to one side
unusual noises or vibrations when driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag and rollover sensor system can cause the airbags to not deploy in the event of an accident, which can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbags do not deploy in the event of an accident
the rollover sensor does not detect a rollover.
